			<div><strong>Spell Book request</strong><br />&nbsp;</div>
		
		
		
		<div>I really like this streamlined spellbook:<br />
<br />
<a href="http://newui.technosapien.net/screen_shots/072502/spellbook_new.jpg" target="_blank">http://newui.technosapien.net/scree...ellbook_new.jpg</a><br />
<br />
But one thing added would make it perfect. In the old UI, I was used to the spell icons being lined up alongside the spell book, and that's where I would click  to memorize new spells. The new spell book has no spell icons next to it, so I find myself kind of looking around for a place to put the spell. <br />
<br />
What would be great is if someone would consider making a streamlined spellbook, like the one above, with the spells window attached to it's left side. <br />
<br />
What do you think? Is it possible?</div>
